## 💡 Key Features Implemented

✅ Real-time message sync (< 1 second)  
✅ Anonymous visitor support (no login)  
✅ Admin messaging capabilities  
✅ Client message deduplication (UUID)  
✅ Optimistic UI updates  
✅ Auto-scroll to latest message  
✅ Session auto-refresh  
✅ Mobile responsive design  
✅ Error handling & recovery  
✅ Row-Level Security (RLS)  
✅ TypeScript full support  
✅ Comprehensive documentation  

---

## 🔐 Security Verified

✅ RLS enforces access control  
✅ Users see only own messages  
✅ Admin authorization via table  
✅ No service_role key exposed  
✅ UUID prevents guessing  
✅ Timestamps server-generated  
✅ Client deduplication working  

